      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not quite sure actually. This is based on the previous implementation. From the milo code, I can tell that it\u0027s from the buildset tag. But the buildset tag is returned from buildbucket. Not quite sure whether it\u0027s output.gitiles_commit or input.gitiles_commit. I\u0027ll try to look it up.",
