      "writtenOn": "2020-08-19T05:55:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e comment to say that it depends on the buildset tag\n\nYeah, I think this is probably the clearest; Indicate that the API is serving based on the buildset tag, and that currently (as of 20Q2), buildbucket sets this based on input.gitiles_commit and scheduler sets this based on its trigger conditions.\n\nI wonder if it would be better for Milo to keep its own index for a combined input.gitiles_commit plus output.gitiles_commit?",
